sky.mix.uk.title: PL Greatest Games: B'ming/A.Villa

sky.mix.uk.title: PL Greatest: WBA v Man Utd 2013

sky.mix.uk.title: PL Greatest: Cardiff v Liverpool

sky.mix.uk.title: Best of Wenger: L'pool/Arsenal 09

sky.mix.uk.title: The Rise Of MVG (2013)

sky.mix.uk.title: Gary Anderson: Back2Back Champion

sky.mix.uk.title: Rob Cross: A Year To Remember 2018

sky.mix.uk.title: Peter Wright: Double Champ 20 & 22

sky.mix.uk.title: EFL 15/16: QPR v Middlesbrough

sky.mix.uk.title: EFL 15/16: B'ham v Middlesbrough
sky.mix.uk.description: Relive some classic action from the English Football League. Here, Birmingham City take on Middlesbrough at St Andrew's in a four-goal thriller in the 2015-16 season.

sky.mix.uk.title: EFL 15/16:Middlesbrough v Brighton
sky.mix.uk.description: A look back at some classic matches from the English Football League. Here, Middlesbrough take on Brighton and Hove Albion in a tense Championship promotion decider in May 2016.

sky.mix.uk.title: EFL 16/17: Aston Villa v N. Forest

E4Plus1.uk.description: The Proton Displacement: Sheldon is jealous when Professor Proton asks Leonard to read his latest publication, so he befriends a TV personality from a rival science show. (S7 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Itchy Brain Simulation: Leonard worries that Sheldon will overreact when he confesses that he failed to return a DVD to the rental shop seven years earlier. (S7 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Thanksgiving Decoupling: Howard takes the gang to his mother's house for Thanksgiving to protect himself from his grumpy father-in-law who has also been invited. (S7 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Discovery Dissipation: Sheldon feels guilty when he gets attention for his accidental discovery of a new element. Raj stays with Howard and Bernadette for a week. (S7 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Your Honor: Captain Holt's mother seeks help from the precinct. Jeffords, Diaz and Boyle redecorate the breakroom. Santiago teaches Gina how to change a tyre. (S4 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Slaughterhouse: Peralta and Diaz try to earn the respect of their idol, Lt Melanie Hawkins, after accidentally disrupting one of her undercover cases. (S4 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Four Great Women and a Manicure: On a visit to the nail salon, Marge and Lisa discuss whether a woman can be simultaneously clever, powerful and beautiful. (S20 Ep20/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Coming to Homerica: When nearby Ogdenville's unemployed come to Springfield looking for jobs, Mayor Quimby shuts the town's borders and enlists private citizens to guard them. (S20 Ep21/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: More singles take the leap of faith. Sparks fly for some, but one bride riles up her in-laws before she's even got down the aisle! Plus: more honeymoon hoo-ha. (S10 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Hook-Up Reverberation: Raj's honesty about his past comes back to haunt him when his girlfriend Emily gives Penny the cold shoulder. The guys consider an investment. (S8 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Treehouse of Horror XIII: Homer's cloning hammock spirals out of control, and Lisa's meddling leaves Springfield vulnerable to zombie attack. (S14 Ep1/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: How I Spent My Strummer Vacation: Homer goes to a rock 'n' roll camp. When it's time to leave, he just wants to keep rockin' with Mick Jagger, Keith Richards and Lenny Kravitz. (S14 Ep2/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: How the Test Was Won: When Bart gets top marks in a test, Lisa's so shocked that she freezes in her exam. Homer desperately avoids danger after failing to renew his insurance. (S20 Ep11/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Dad-Feelings Limited: As Comic Book Guy and his wife Kumiko debate whether to have a baby, his awesome origin story is revealed. (S32 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates
E4Plus1.uk.description: A tattooist who loves to shoot, a gym bunny, a cheesemaker and a multilingual entrepreneur who loves a man in a suit are all looking for love on their first date. (S20 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: Two more singles get wed, but could a bride's pursuit for perfection jeopardise love? Plus: more honeymoon hubbub as one groom threatens the chance of romance. (S10 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Naked Attraction
E4Plus1.uk.description: Professional dancer and virgin Raheem wants a man who can pop some moves on the dancefloor and in the bedroom. Rugby player Jerome needs a confidence boost to find his lucky lady. (S7 Ep4)

Film4.uk.title: Infinite
Film4.uk.description: (2021) Sci-fi action. Mark Wahlberg discovers that his hallucinations are memories from past lives. There are others like him, but they don't all have good intentions...

Film4.uk.title: Team America: World Police
Film4.uk.description: (2004) Outrageous satirical comedy from the South Park team. A crack team of puppets battle to save the world from an evil terrorist plot hatched by North Korean leader Kim Jong Il.

Film4.uk.title: Antwone Fisher
Film4.uk.description: (2002) Real-life drama with Denzel Washington. In trying to uncover the reason for recruit Antwone Fisher's violence, a naval psychiatrist uncovers a history of child abuse.

Film4.uk.title: Teleshopping
Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: Teleshopping
Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: All the King's Men
Film4.uk.description: (1949) Drama with John Ireland. A local politician begins to lust for the kind of power he used to hold to account. He should be careful how he treats people on the way to the top...

Film4.uk.title: Mandy
Film4.uk.description: (1952) Poignant Ealing drama starring seven-year-old Mandy Miller as a deaf girl whose parents - played by Phyllis Calvert and Terence Morgan - fight over her treatment.

Film4.uk.title: The Swimmer
Film4.uk.description: (1968) Burt Lancaster stars as the angst-ridden middle-aged man who decides to swim home via neighbour's pools in Frank and Eleanor Perry's superb allegorical drama.

Film4.uk.title: Footsteps in the Fog
Film4.uk.description: (1955) Atmospheric Victorian melodrama. Stewart Granger plays a sinister aristocrat who poisons his wife. However, his maid (Jean Simmons) knows his secret and tries to use it against him.

Film4.uk.title: Cowboys & Aliens
Film4.uk.description: (2011) Sci-fi western starring Daniel Craig and Harrison Ford. A brutal cattle baron and his amnesiac enemy must cease their feuding when a town is attacked by aliens.

Film4.uk.title: Good Luck to You, Leo Grande
Film4.uk.description: (2022) Drama starring Emma Thompson as a recently widowed, retired teacher who has a sexual bucket list she wants to get around to now that she has the time and, perhaps, even the energy.

Film4.uk.title: Fresh
Film4.uk.description: (2022) Adults only horror with Daisy Edgar-Jones. When date-weary Noa meets a guy in a supermarket, she thinks things are looking up. But he's oddly obsessed with not eating animals...

Film4.uk.title: The Riot Club
Film4.uk.description: (2014) Dark drama about the members of an elite Oxford University drinking society. Starring Sam Claflin, Max Irons and Holliday Grainger. Sex/very strong language/drugs/violence.

Film4.uk.title: Teleshopping
Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: Teleshopping
Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: 3:10 to Yuma
Film4.uk.description: (1957) Classic western with Glenn Ford and Van Heflin. The capture of a murderous stagecoach robber propels an impoverished local rancher on a perilous journey. Directed by Delmer Daves.

Film4.uk.title: The Man from Colorado
Film4.uk.description: (1948) Western. When a sadistic Union colonel (Glenn Ford) becomes a federal judge after the Civil War, his friend (William Holden) takes the deputy job to try and temper his actions.

Film4.uk.title: Mission: Impossible - Fallout...
Film4.uk.description: ...Interview Special: Tom Cruise, Rebecca Ferguson, Henry Cavill, Simon Pegg, Vanessa Kirby and director Christopher McQuarrie talk about making the sixth instalment in the thriller series.

Film4.uk.title: Kind Hearts and Coronets
Film4.uk.description: (1949) This dark comedy from Ealing studios sees Alec Guinness take on the roles of eight characters, all the noble victims of a vengeance-seeking relative, played by Dennis Price.

Film4.uk.title: Titanic
Film4.uk.description: (1997) Leonardo DiCaprio and Kate Winslet star in James Cameron's Oscar-winning epic. Lovers from across the social divide meet on the doomed luxury liner.

Film4.uk.title: The Contractor
Film4.uk.description: (2022) Action thriller with Chris Pine. An ex-soldier takes on private work to feed his family, but finds himself in dire straits (danger; not the band). With Kiefer Sutherland.

Film4.uk.title: How to Blow Up a Pipeline
Film4.uk.description: (2022) High-octane eco-thriller. A disparate group of young Americans unite to disrupt the oil industry in an act motivated by everything from the ideological to the downright personal.

Film4.uk.title: Woman at War
Film4.uk.description: (2018) Dark comedy with Halldra Geirhardsdttir. A choir teacher living in a small town in Iceland has a secret identity: 'Mountain Woman', a human-sized eco-superhero. In Icelandic/subs.

Film4.uk.title: Teleshopping
Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: Teleshopping
Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: Ten Tall Men
Film4.uk.description: (1951) Comedy adventure. Burt Lancaster stars as a Foreign Legion sergeant leading nine men on a dangerous mission to prevent a Berber attack on a North African desert fort.

Film4.uk.title: Payroll
Film4.uk.description: (1961) British crime thriller starring Billie Whitelaw. When Jackie's husband - an armoured van driver - is killed in a heist, she vows to unmask those responsible and take her revenge.

Film4.uk.title: Three Hours to Kill
Film4.uk.description: (1954) Western starring Dana Andrews. A man falsely accused of murder gets a last-minute reprieve from the lynch mob so he can track down the real culprit.

Film4.uk.title: Born Free
Film4.uk.description: (1966) Gem of a family drama based on a true story. After a life in captivity, can lioness Elsa learn to survive in the wild? Starring Virginia McKenna and John Barry's Oscar-winning score.

Film4.uk.title: Jumanji: The Next Level
Film4.uk.description: (2019) Adventure comedy sequel with Dwayne Johnson, Jack Black, Kevin Hart and Karen Gillan. The old school pals enter the Jumanji video game again to save their friend.

Film4.uk.title: Deadpool 2
Film4.uk.description: (2018) Ryan Reynolds returns as the potty-mouthed, can of whup-ass-opening superhero and now he's got buddies to help him take on baddie Josh Brolin in the all-out action comedy sequel.

Film4.uk.title: Carlito's Way
Film4.uk.description: (1993) Brian De Palma's crime thriller with Al Pacino. An ex-con, fresh out of jail, flamboyantly declares his plan to go straight. But his criminal past just won't let him go...

More4Plus1.uk.title: Four in a Bed

More4Plus1.uk.title: Four in a Bed

More4Plus1.uk.title: Four in a Bed
